<!-- ══════ FAQ ══════ -->
<section class="faq-section">
  <div class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-line"></span><span class="eyebrow-text">Common Questions</span></div>
  <h2 class="section-title">FREQUENTLY<br>ASKED<br>QUESTIONS.</h2>
  <div class="gold-rule"></div>
  <div class="faq-list">
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">How much does drywall installation cost in Halifax?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></button>
      <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">Cost depends on the scope — a small patch is very affordable, while a full basement drywall project is priced per square foot of area. We provide free, itemized quotes after seeing the space so there are no surprises.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">Can you fix a single hole or do you only do full drywall projects?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></button>
      <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">We handle everything — from a single nail pop or small hole to a full room installation. No job is too small. If you have several patches needed around the house, we can knock them all out in one visit.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">How long does drywall mud take to dry before painting?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></button>
      <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">Standard drywall compound needs about 24 hours per coat under normal conditions (good ventilation, room temperature). Most projects need two to three coats, so budget three to seven days between finishing and painting. We'll advise on the timeline for your specific project.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">Do you handle basement drywall in Halifax?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></button>
      <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">Yes — basement drywall is one of our most common projects across HRM. We address moisture concerns, install proper framing where needed, hang, tape, and finish to a paint-ready surface.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">What does a drywall quote from ETRA include?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></button>
      <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">Our quotes cover materials and labour for the agreed scope of work. If anything unexpected comes up — like damaged framing behind the wall — we discuss it with you before proceeding. Our pricing is transparent and honest.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

